title: Harley Quinn In Batman: Streets Of Gotham
description:
Every issue of Batman: Streets Of Gotham, featuring Harley Quinn

As a new Batman rises on the streets of Gotham City, the heroes, villains and citizens take notice. How will the police feel about this new Batman, and can he control the crime in Gotham the way the old Batman did?

Issue #1 ("Ignition!" & "Strange Bedfellows")

Issue #5 ("Leviathan Part One")

Issue #17 ("The House of Hush, Chapter Two: Reunions" & "Ashes To Ashes, Part One: Smoldering Embers")
